{"thag6.13:0.1":"Theragatha 6.13 ","thag6.13:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.13:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.13:0.4":"Sirimandattheragatha ","thag6.13:1.1":"“Channamativassati, ","thag6.13:1.2":"vivatam nativassati; ","thag6.13:1.3":"Tasma channam vivaretha, ","thag6.13:1.4":"evam tam nativassati. ","thag6.13:2.1":"Maccunabbhahato loko, ","thag6.13:2.2":"jaraya parivarito; ","thag6.13:2.3":"Tanhasallena otinno, ","thag6.13:2.4":"icchadhupayito sada. ","thag6.13:3.1":"Maccunabbhahato loko, ","thag6.13:3.2":"parikkhitto jaraya ca; ","thag6.13:3.3":"Hannati niccamattano, ","thag6.13:3.4":"pattadandova takkaro. ","thag6.13:4.1":"Agacchantaggikhandhava, ","thag6.13:4.2":"maccu byadhi jara tayo; ","thag6.13:4.3":"Paccuggantum balam natthi, ","thag6.13:4.4":"javo natthi palayitum. ","thag6.13:5.1":"Amogham divasam kayira, ","thag6.13:5.2":"appena bahukena va; ","thag6.13:5.3":"Yam yam vijahate rattim, ","thag6.13:5.4":"tadunam tassa jivitam. ","thag6.13:6.1":"Carato titthato vapi, ","thag6.13:6.2":"asinasayanassa va; ","thag6.13:6.3":"Upeti carima ratti, ","thag6.13:6.4":"na te kalo pamajjitun”ti. ","thag6.13:6.5":"… Sirimando thero …. "}